00:06:33.359 --> 00:06:35.440
and he does say that, but I believe that he reveals

00:06:35.440 --> 00:06:37.920
something that is absolutely imperative for us

00:06:37.920 --> 00:06:40.100
to understand this evening, and what it is

00:06:40.100 --> 00:06:42.260
