00:07:29.899 --> 00:07:33.179
many times, you begin to think about the call to ministry,

00:07:33.179 --> 00:07:37.820
he would simply say this, follow me, follow me,

00:07:37.820 --> 00:07:40.779
and straightway, immediately, they left their nets,

00:07:40.779 --> 00:07:42.100
