00:08:12.579 --> 00:08:15.779
He says, be followers of me, but then he says,

00:08:15.779 --> 00:08:20.420
even as I also am of Christ.

00:08:20.420 --> 00:08:23.140
The apostle Paul was following the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:08:23.140 --> 00:08:25.600
You begin to look at his life, and you begin to study

00:08:25.600 --> 00:08:28.059
