00:08:36.580 --> 00:08:39.340
Begin to look at this thought of following Jesus

00:08:39.340 --> 00:08:42.460
and understanding that we each have been called

00:08:42.460 --> 00:08:45.260
to be followers of Jesus Christ.

00:08:45.260 --> 00:08:46.979
